@Franklyaghost @LadySta48470651 @TheNomiGirl @KaizenKitten @TestamentOfDark Born in Lichtenberg, we lived in Marzahn and before I was born my family lived in Treptow.
So everything in the easternmost east of Berlin. 
Honestly, I have to say I haven't been there for many years and I don't know my way around there very well.

@MomExpat @RubyDarcy2015 It's painful to watch. Swarms of hipsters forcing the original ppl out of their Kiez. These ppl move to where I live now which is the very east of Berlin (Marzahn-Hellersdorf).
It was kinda annoying when I moved here already and became way worse.
